cs.SI, cs.CL, cs.CY, cs.DL, cs.SD 

The paper discusses two computational models for analyzing political attention in social media, which involves natural language processing and machine learning techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.SI (Social and Information Networks), followed by cs.CL (Computation and Language) and cs.CY (Computers and Society). Additionally, the paper also involves deep learning techniques, which could fall under cs.DL (Machine Learning) and cs.SD (Software Engineering).
